  <entry>
    <title>OpenCV-Day3</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/12/30/OpenCV-Day3/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/12/30/OpenCV-Day3/</id>
    <published>2021-12-30T06:23:02.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-12-30T08:41:23.848Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>每天学习opencv - day3</p><span id="more"></span><h3 id="图像阈值">图像阈值</h3><p>ret, dst = cv2.threshold(src, thresh, maxval, type)<br>src : 输入图， 只能输入单通道图像,一般来说是灰度图<br>dst : 输出图<br>thresh : 阈值， 通常情况取127<br>maxval : 最大值， 一般取255， 当像素超过了阈值（或者小于阈值， 根据type来决定）， 所赋予的值<br>tyoe : 选择的方法，怎么判断阈值<br>cv2.THRESH_BINARY 超过阈值部分去maxval, 否则取0<br>cv2.THRESH_BINARY_INV THRESH_BINARY的反转<br>cv2.THRESH_TRUNC 大于阈值的部分设为阈值， 否则不变<br>cv2.THRESH_TOZERO 大于阈值的部分不改变， 否则设为0<br>cv2.THRESH_TOZERO_INV THRESH_TOZERO的反转</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ret1, dst1 = cv2.threshold(img, <span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, cv2.THRESH_BINARY)</span><br><span class="line">ret2, dst2 = cv2.threshold(img, <span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, cv2.THRESH_BINARY_INV)</span><br><span class="line">ret3, dst3 = cv2.threshold(img, <span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, cv2.THRESH_TRUNC)</span><br><span class="line">ret4, dst4 = cv2.threshold(img, <span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, cv2.THRESH_TOZERO)</span><br><span class="line">ret5, dst5 = cv2.threshold(img, <span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, cv2.THRESH_TOZERO_INV)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">titles = [<span class="string">&#x27;Origin&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;BINARY&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;BINARY_INV&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;TRUNC&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;TOZERO&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;TOZERO_INV&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">images = [img, dst1, dst2, dst3, dst4, dst5]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(images)):</span><br><span class="line">    plt.subplot(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, i + <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.imshow(images[i], <span class="string">&#x27;gray&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.title(titles[i])</span><br><span class="line">    plt.xticks([]), plt.yticks([])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="C:\Users\程序猿代码狗软件工程狮\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20211230145656442.png" alt="对比图" style="zoom: 50%;" /><h3 id="图像平滑">图像平滑</h3><h4 id="增加噪音">增加噪音</h4><p>salt and pepper noise，图像的像素点由于噪声影响随机变成了黑点（dark spot）或白点（white spot）。图像的像素点的强度值改为黑点或者白点，黑点的强度值是0，白点的强度值是255。原始图像的强度值区间是[0, 255]，那么噪声函数中相应点是255或者是-255，加起来就可以达到是0或255的效果。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">row, column = img.shape</span><br><span class="line">noise_salt = np.random.randint(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">256</span>, (row, column))</span><br><span class="line">noise_pepper = np.random.randint(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">256</span>, (row, column))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 10%的盐噪声和椒噪声函数矩阵</span></span><br><span class="line">rand = <span class="number">0.1</span></span><br><span class="line">noise_salt = np.where(noise_salt &lt; rand * <span class="number">256</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">noise_pepper = np.where(noise_pepper &lt; rand * <span class="number">256</span>, -<span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>opencv的图像矩阵类型是uint8，低于0和高于255的值并不截断，而是使用了模操作。即200+60=260 % 256 = 4。所以我们需要先将原始图像矩阵和噪声图像矩阵都转成浮点数类型进行相加操作，然后再转回来。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">img.astype(<span class="string">&quot;float&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">noise_salt.astype(<span class="string">&quot;float&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">noise_pepper.astype(<span class="string">&quot;float&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">salt = img + noise_salt</span><br><span class="line">pepper = img + noise_pepper</span><br><span class="line">salt = np.where(salt &gt; <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, salt)</span><br><span class="line">pepper = np.where(pepper &lt; <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, pepper)</span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&quot;salt&quot;</span>, salt.astype(<span class="string">&quot;uint8&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&quot;pepper&quot;</span>, pepper.astype(<span class="string">&quot;uint8&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">cv2.waitKey()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\salt.jpg" alt="salt" style="zoom: 25%;" /><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\pepper.jpg" alt="pepper" style="zoom:25%;" /><h4 id="滤波处理">滤波处理</h4><h5 id="均值滤波">均值滤波</h5><p>简单的平均卷积操作， 构建内积， 求得平均</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">blur = cv2.blur(salt.astype(<span class="string">&quot;uint8&quot;</span>), (<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>))</span><br><span class="line">cv_show(<span class="string">&#x27;blur&#x27;</span>, blur)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\blur.jpg" alt="blur" style="zoom:25%;" /><h5 id="方框滤波">方框滤波</h5><p>归一化产生的结果和均值滤波产生结果一致</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">box = cv2.boxFilter(salt.astype(<span class="string">&quot;uint8&quot;</span>), -<span class="number">1</span>, (<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>), normalize = <span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\box.jpg" alt="box" style="zoom:25%;" /><p>不选择归一化</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">non_box = cv2.boxFilter(salt.astype(&quot;uint8&quot;), -1, (3, 3), normalize = False)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>发生越界，直接取到255</p><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\non_box.jpg" alt="non_box" style="zoom:25%;" /><h5 id="高斯滤波">高斯滤波</h5><p>高斯模糊的卷积盒内的数值满足高斯分布，越靠近值越大</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gaussian = cv2.GaussianBlur(salt.astype(<span class="string">&quot;uint8&quot;</span>), (<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">5</span>), <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\gaussian.jpg" alt="gaussian" style="zoom:25%;" /><h5 id="中值滤波">中值滤波</h5><p>用中位数进行替代</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">median = cv2.medianBlur(salt.astype(&quot;uint8&quot;), 5)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\median.jpg" alt="median" style="zoom:25%;" /><h5 id="vhstack拼接图片">_vhstack拼接图片</h5><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">res = np.hstack((blur, gaussian, median))</span><br><span class="line">res1 = np.vstack((blur, gaussian, median))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="F:%5CMyblog%5Cblog%5Csource_posts%5COpenCV-Day3%5Call.jpg" alt="all"></p><img src="F:\Myblog\blog\source\_posts\OpenCV-Day3\all1.jpg" alt="all1" style="zoom:25%;" />]]></content>
    
    
